---
import Layout from '@/layouts/main.astro'
---

<Layout title="Support">
  <section class="min-h-screen pt-40 pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto typo text-on-surface-variant typo-headings:text-primary typo-headings:font-serif typo-headings:italic typo-strong:text-on-surface-variant typo-blockquote:text-primary">
      <h1 class="text-center">Support</h1>
      <p>Thank you for using Spendful. If you have questions, need help, or want to report an issue, we’re here to help.</p>
      <p>
        You can contact us anytime at: 📧
        <a href="mailto:buihdk@gmail.com" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline">buihdk@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>We typically respond within 1–2 business days.</p>
      <p>Spendful is designed to be a calm, private spending journal. Your data stays on your device unless you choose to export it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
